item.title: CVE-2022-4297|2024-08-03T01:34:49.994Z -- unknown -- wp%20autocomplete%20search
item.description: The WP AutoComplete Search WordPress plugin through 1.0.4 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement via an AJAX available to unauthenticated users, leading to an unauthenticated SQL injection
